Package models.Phase.MapEditing

Class MapEditing

java.lang.Object
models.Phase.Phase
models.Phase.MapEditing.MapEditing
Direct Known Subclasses:
Postload, Preload
public abstract class MapEditing extends Phase
The MapEditing abstract class extends Phase and provides common functionalities for different stages of the map editing process. It allows for loading, editing, saving maps, and displaying map information.
